        "text": "=‚ö†Ô∏è‚ö†Ô∏è‚ö†Ô∏è\nHey *{{ $json.username }}*, You have a task due *TODAY*! Take the appropriate action ASAP!!!\n‚ö†Ô∏è‚ö†Ô∏è‚ö†Ô∏è\n\n*------------------------------------------------------------------------------*\nüìù *Card Name*: {{ $json.cardName }}\nüìì *Board Name*: {{ $json.boardName }}\nüîó *Card URL*: [Link]({{ $json.url }})\n‚è∞ *Due Date*: {{ $json.dueDate }}\n*------------------------------------------------------------------------------*\n\nFrom the Trello Bot.",
